T1  - Trade and search generated unemployment
AU  - Davidson, Carl
AU  - Martin, Lawrence
AU  - Matusz, Steven
JO  - Journal of International Economics
VL  - 48
IS  - 2
SP  - 271
EP  - 299
PY  - 1999
DA  - 1999/08/01/
